                        <p>Buffett considers interest rates' impact on business valuation and investment returns. Low rates can distort valuations.</p>

                        <h3>Valuation Impact</h3>
                        <p>Interest rates affect discount rates used in business valuation. Low rates can make stocks appear more attractive than they really are.</p>

                        <h3>Business Effects</h3>
                        <p>Interest rates affect borrowing costs and economic activity. Companies with strong balance sheets benefit most during high-rate environments.</p>

                        <h3>Investment Implications</h3>
                        <p>Be cautious when interest rates are very low, as future rate increases can pressure valuations.</p>
                    `
                },
                'us-economy': {
                    title: 'The US Economy',
                    content: `
                        <p>Buffett maintains an optimistic long-term view of the US economy, believing in its fundamental strength and ability to grow over time.</p>

                        <h3>Long-term Optimism</h3>
                        <p>Buffett believes the US economy will continue growing over decades due to innovation, demographics, and institutional strengths.</p>

                        <h3>Short-term Fluctuations</h3>
                        <p>While short-term economic cycles occur, Buffett focuses on businesses that can thrive regardless of economic conditions.</p>

                        <h3>Competitive Advantages</h3>
                        <p>The US economy benefits from strong property rights, rule of law, and entrepreneurial culture.</p>
                    `
                },
                'philanthropy': {
                    title: 'Philanthropy',
                    content: `
                        <p>Buffett has pledged to give away 99% of his wealth during his lifetime. He believes that those who are fortunate should help others who are less fortunate.</p>

                        <h3>Philanthropic Commitment</h3>
                        <p>Buffett signed the Giving Pledge, committing to donate the majority of his wealth to charitable causes during his lifetime.</p>

                        <h3>Social Responsibility</h3>
                        <p>Wealth brings responsibility. Those who have been fortunate have an obligation to help those less fortunate.</p>

                        <h3>Impactful Giving</h3>
                        <p>Buffett focuses on high-impact giving. He supports causes that can create lasting positive change in the world.</p>
                    `
                },
                'public-pension': {
                    title: 'Public Pension',
                    content: `
