                        <h3>Funding Shortfalls</h3>
                        <p>Many public pension funds are significantly underfunded, creating future liabilities for taxpayers.</p>

                        <h3>Economic Impact</h3>
                        <p>Underfunded pensions can lead to higher taxes, reduced services, or benefit cuts for retirees.</p>

                        <h3>Policy Solutions</h3>
                        <p>Governments need to address pension funding gaps through increased contributions and realistic benefit promises.</p>
                    `
