                    <p><em>[Warren Buffett, 2011 Letter to Shareholders]</em></p>
                    
                    <hr>
                    
                    <p>Charlie and I believe that those entrusted with handling the funds of others should establish performance goals at the onset of their stewardship. Lacking such standards, managements are tempted to shoot the arrow of performance and then paint the bull’s-eye around wherever it lands.</p>
                    
